listingDetails.title: Experience the Allure of a Stunning 2-BD in La Mer
listingDetails.title_l1: شقة في برج لا ريف 1،لا ريف،بورت دو لا مير،لا مير،جميرا 2 غرف 12000 درهم - 7592201
listingDetails.title_l2: Jumeirah，La Mer，Port De La Mer，La Rive，La Rive Tower 1 2 卧室 12000 AED - 7592201
listingDetails.description:
Welcome to La Rive - Port De La Mer, where luxury and comfort blend seamlessly in this exquisite 2-bedroom apartment. From the moment you step inside, you\'ll be captivated by the thoughtful design and attention to detail. 


As you enter the apartment, you\'ll be greeted by a spacious living room that exudes elegance and offers a breathtaking view of the sea through a charming balcony. The natural light floods the room, creating a vibrant and serene ambiance. The open concept design seamlessly connects the living and dining area, providing a harmonious space for relaxation and entertainment. Whether you\'re enjoying a cozy movie night or hosting a gathering, this area is perfect for creating lasting memories with loved ones. 


The interior of the apartment combines modern finishes with a Farmhouse theme, creating a unique and inviting atmosphere. The fully equipped kitchen boasts top-of-the-line appliances, making it a haven for any culinary enthusiast. Whether you\'re preparing a quick breakfast or hosting a dinner party, this kitchen is up to the task. 


The two generously sized bedrooms offer a tranquil retreat, each boasting an en-suite bathroom and ample closet space. The bathrooms are adorned with high-end fixtures and finishes, elevating the luxurious feel of the apartment. You\'ll find that every detail has been carefully considered to ensure your utmost comfort and style. 


Additionally, the apartment features a guest toilet and a laundry room, providing convenience and practicality for your everyday needs. 


Key Features:
Complimentary weekly cleaning
Free Wi-Fi with smart TV
Fully equipped kitchen
Towels and bed linens provided
All utilities (DEWA, Etisalat, Gas, Chiller) included in the price
Free assigned parking space


Amenities:
Gymnasium
Swimming pool
24-hour security staff


Included in Price:
All utilities (DEWA, Etisalat, gas, chiller)
Access to building/community facilities like the pool and gym


Additional Fees/Taxes:
5% VAT
Dubai Tourism Fee (AED 20 per night for the first 30 nights)
Refundable security deposit: AED 5,000
Rental Fee are subject to change based on season and availability


Optional Services:
Extra Bed is available upon request (AED 150 per night for stays up to 6 nights, AED 100 per night for stays over 6 nights)
Complimentary baby cot (subject to availability)


*Non-smoking/no pet policy enforced.
